                "invention-title": [
                    "Combined hydrogen-mixed low-carbon combustion device and control method thereof",
                    "一种组合式混氢低碳燃烧装置及其控制方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to the technical field of energy-saving combustion of metallurgical industry furnaces, in particular to a combined hydrogen-mixed low-carbon combustion device and a control method thereof. The device mainly comprises a hydrogen valve group, a gas valve group, an air valve group, a burner, an igniter and a guide plate. The hydrogen valve group comprises a hydrogen regulating valve and a hydrogen flow meter; the fuel gas valve group comprises a fuel gas regulating valve, a fuel gas flowmeter and a fuel gas component on-line detector, and the fuel gas component on-line detector is mounted on a fuel gas pipeline; the air valve group comprises an air regulating valve and an air flow meter; hydrogen is mixed during fuel combustion, an existing heating furnace combustion device is transformed, and hydrogen-mixed combustion is achieved; according to the invention, all the valve groups are mutually coordinated and matched with the flow control valve to control the air inlet amount, and the temperature monitoring device monitors the air inlet temperature, so that the effects of reducing pollutant emission and increasing the energy utilization rate are achieved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及冶金工业炉窑节能燃烧技术领域，具体涉及一种组合式混氢低碳燃烧装置及其控制方法。本发明主要包括氢气阀组、燃气阀组、空气阀组、燃烧器、点火器、导流板。氢气阀组包括氢气调节阀、氢气流量计；燃气阀组包括燃气调节阀、燃气流量计、燃气成分在线检测仪，其中燃气成分在线监测仪安装在燃气管道上；空气阀组包括空气调节阀、空气流量计；本发明通过在燃料燃烧时混入氢气，改造现有加热炉燃烧装置，实现了混氢燃烧；本发明通过各个阀组之间相互协调，配合流量控制阀控制进气量，以及温度监测装置监测进气温度，达到了降低污染物排放，增加能量利用率的效果。"
                }
            ]
